  * Add additional precondition checks to `rt::integer::bits`. (Benjamin Bannier, Corelight)

  * Consistently use `ntohX` type functions for `rt::integer::ntohX`. (Benjamin Bannier, Corelight)

0.4.0-681 | 2020-07-23 14:55:25 +0000

